    "Course starts in {time_remaining_string} on {course_start_date}.": "\u05d4\u05e7\u05d5\u05e8\u05e1 \u05de\u05ea\u05d7\u05d9\u05dc \u05d1-{time_remaining_string} \u05d1-{course_start_date}.",
